  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Solon Capital Holdings is an investment holding company based in Sierra Leone, with four investments in Sierra Leone, Liberia, Guinea and Cote d&#x2019;Ivoire. Businesses in Sierra Leone struggle to raise the capital they need to grow. By using a permanent capital vehicle, Solon can offer greater flexibility and longer-term financing to the businesses it invests in. Our investment in Solon will open up the opportunity to successfully grow businesses over the long-term, delivering economic growth and creating direct and indirect jobs.</narrative>
  </description>
